            "text": "<p>Hammitt is committed to providing a website that is accessible to everyone. <\/p><p>We are actively working to achieve all standards of the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.0 AA. The WCAG 2.0 AA explains how to make web content more accessible for people with different abilities. <strong> <\/strong><\/p><p>We are also always seeking out feedback and solutions that will continue to improve our overall website accessibility.  <\/p><p>If you experience any difficulty in accessing our website, notice any content, feature, or functionality that you believe is not fully accessible to people with disabilities, or simply have suggestions or feedback regarding the accessibility of our website, please contact us by:<\/p><p><strong>Calling:<\/strong> 800-764-3119 (Monday-Friday, 9am-5pm PST)<\/p><p><strong>E-mailing:<\/strong> wecare@hammitt.com with “Website Accessibility” in the subject line and provide a description of the specific feature you feel is not fully accessible or a suggestion for improvement.<\/p><p><strong>Sending a letter to:<\/strong> Hammitt, 2101 Pacific Coast Highway, Hermosa Beach, CA 90254, Attn: Accessibility Department.  Please provide a description of the specific feature you feel is not fully accessible or a suggestion for improvement.<\/p><p>We take your feedback seriously and will consider it as we evaluate ways to accommodate all of our customers and our overall accessibility policies. Additionally, while we do not control such vendors, we strongly encourage vendors of third-party digital content to provide content that is accessible and user friendly.<\/p><p><strong>THIRD-PARTY SITES<\/strong><\/p><p>Throughout this website, we make use of different third-party websites such as Instagram, Zoom, Twitter, and Facebook to spread news and information about www.hammitt.com's products and services. These sites, which are not controlled by www.hammitt.com, may present challenges for individuals with disabilities that we are not able to control or remedy.<\/p><p>As made publicly available, here are the Accessibility Policies provided from these third-party sites:<\/p><p> <\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/help\/141636465971794\/\">Facebook Accessibility Policy<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/accessibility\">Zoom Accessibility Policy<\/a><\/p>"
